                "backing. Subsequently 22Ne ions were implanted into",
                "the porous surface with an incident dose of approx.",
                "1 C. The incident 22Ne ion energy was 75 keV,",
                "corresponding to a target thickness of  cca 95 keV",
                "for an alpha-particle beam of 828-keV energy"
              ]
